# Sign Language Detection with Audio

This project uses OpenCV, MediaPipe, and a custom-trained Keras model to detect hand gestures and speak them aloud using text-to-speech.

## Features
- Detects 7 hand gestures (Hello, I love you, No, Okay, Please, Thank you, Yes)
- Converts detected gestures to speech
- Allows choosing between male or female voice

## How to Run

1. Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt 
2. Run the script: 

  predict.py
